quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,158,aur khuwa tum mrw ya maaray jao bahar haal tum sab ko simat kar jana Allah hi ki taraf hai
3,159,"(ae Peghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) yeh Allah ki barri rehmat hai ke tum inn logon ke liye bohat naram mizaaj waqay hue ho warna agar kahin tum tund khoo aur sang dil hotay to yeh sab tumahray gardo paish se chaatt jatay inn ke qasoor maaf kar do, inn ke haq mein dua ye mughfirat karo, aur deen ke kaam mein un ko bhi shareek mahswara rakho, phir jab tumhara azm kisi raye par mustahkam ho jaye to Allah par bharosa karo, Allah ko woh log pasand hain jo usi ke bharoosay par kaam karte hain"
3,160,"Allah tumhari madad par ho to koi taaqat tum par ghalib anay wali nahi, aur woh tumhe chore day, to is ke baad kon hai jo tumhari madad karsaktha ho? pas jo sachey momin hain un ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
3,161,"kisi nabi ka yeh kaam nahi ho sakta ke woh khayanat kar jaye aur jo koi khayanat kere to woh apni khayanat sameit qayamat ke roz haazir ho jaye ga, phir har mutnaqas ko is ki kamaai ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur kisi par kuch zulm nah hoga"
3,162,bhala yeh kaisay ho sakta hai ke jo shakhs hamesha Allah ki Raza par chalne wala ho woh uss shakhs ke se kaam kere jo Allah ke ghazab mein ghar gaya ho aur jis ka aakhri thikana jahannum ho jo bad tareen thikana hai ?
3,163,Allah ke nazdeek dono qisam ke admio-n mein badarjahafarq hai aur Allah sab ke aamaal par nazar rakhta hai
3,164,"dar haqeeqat ahal imaan par to Allah ne yeh bohat bara ahsaan kya hai ke unn ke darmain khud unhi mein se aik aisa paighambar uthaya jo is ki ayaat inhen sunataa hai, unn ki zindagion ko sanwarta hai aur unn ko kitaab aur danai ki taleem deta hai, halaank is se pehlay yahi log Sarih gmrahyon mein parre hue thay"
3,165,"aur yeh tumhara kya haal hai ke jab tum par museebat aa pari to tum kehnay lagey yeh kahan se aayi? halaank ( jung badar mein ) is se daal o gani museebat tumahray hathon ( fareeq mukhalif par ) par chuki hai ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn se kaho, yeh museebat tumhari apni layi hui hai, Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
